Package: zerosdr
Architecture: armhf
Depends: libasound2 (>= 1.0.18), libc6 (>= 2.31), libgcc-s1 | libgcc1, librtlsdr0 (>= 0.6.0), libstdc++6 (>= 5.2)
Description: Lightweight SDR interface for Raspberry Pi with audio demodulation
 A graphical SDR application optimized for small SPI displays
 on Raspberry Pi. Supports RTL-SDR devices and provides
 spectrum and waterfall visualization with FM/NFM/AM audio demodulation.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time spectrum analyzer and waterfall display
  - FM/NFM/AM audio demodulation
  - Volume control and squelch detection
  - Optimized for Raspberry Pi 3B and newer
